Expose real file ownership, ownership mutations, and process-aware access checks.

WASI Preview 1 filestat omits uid/gid, and the prior access fallback only checked
whether any permission bit existed. Route these operations through agentOS so C
helpers observe the same ownership and DAC decisions as the kernel.

